<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Toollit logo -->
    <div style="margin-top: 20px">
      <a
        href="<%= toollitURL %>"
        style="display: flex; align-items: center; text-decoration: none"
        target="_blank"
      >
        <img
          src="<%= toollitLogo %>"
          alt="Toollit logo"
          width="35px"
          height="35px"
          title="Toollit logo"
        />
        <span style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #000"
          >Toollit</span
        >
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div style="margin-top: 20px">
      <p style="color: black">회원 가입을 위한 인증번호 입니다.</p>
      <p style="color: black">
        아래의 인증 번호를 입력하여 인증을 완료해주세요.
      </p>
      <p
        style="
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          font-size: 15px;
          font-weight: 600;
          margin-top: 15px;
        "
      >
        <span style="padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem">인증번호: </span>
        <span style="background-color: #f2f2f2; padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem">
          <%= authCode %>
        </span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
